This game kind of reminded me of the “Clemson/Ohio.St” game where both “Ohio.St/49ers” jumped out to a decent lead & then they made some stupid mistakes to let both “Clemson/Seahawks” jump back into the game & it actually cost “Ohio.St” the game & almost cost us “49ers”! 7:43 Mostert should have been tackled at the 30 yard line, but two guys missed tackles so he got all the way up to the 45
